        "z": "f297466f3ce2446a",
        "name": "Do the comparison",
        "func": "let k = flow.get(\"k\");\nlet latestOpenWMTemp = flow.get(\"latestOpenWMTemp\");\nlet latestAvg = msg.payload;\nif(Math.abs(latestAvg-latestOpenWMTemp)>k){\n    msg.payload = \"Temperature data is not coherent!\";\n    return msg;\n} else {\n    console.log(\"Coherent!\");\n    return null;\n}\n",
